@host = http://localhost:5001

### Publish an order through the API; Dapr delivers it to POST /subscribe
POST {{host}}/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "ORD-1001",
  "customerId": "CUST-42",
  "orderDate": "2026-05-13T09:30:00Z",
  "lines": [
    {
      "sku": "SKU-AAA",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 19.95
    },
    {
      "sku": "SKU-BBB",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 49.00
    }
  ]
}

### Inspect Dapr's discovered pub/sub subscriptions
GET {{host}}/dapr/subscribe
